<p sourcefile="fundamentals/localization.md" sourcestartlinenumber="146" sourceendlinenumber="146"><a name="error"></a></p>
<p sourcefile="fundamentals/localization.md" sourcestartlinenumber="148" sourceendlinenumber="148">If you are using Visual Studio 2017 Preview version 15.3, you&#39;ll get an error indicator in the resource editor. Remove the <em>ResXFileCodeGenerator</em>  value from the <em>Custom Tool</em>  properties grid to prevent this error message:</p>
